HEADWORD: Dough-baked
<hw>Dough"-baked`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Imperfectly
baked; hence, not brought to perfection; unfinished; also, of weak or
dull understanding.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>
<rj><au>Halliwell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
